Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:46.86,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,400)\blur0.5}駆け抜ける　今の続き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:53.20,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,400)\blur0.5}君が泣いた夜は　その中に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:59.38,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,400)\blur0.5}遠い未来の輝きを隠してた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:04.02,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,400)\blur0.5}静けさが君を待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:10.02,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,400)\blur0.5}眩しい丘　きっと行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:15.70,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,400)\blur0.5}君の　地平へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:21.94,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,800)\blur0.5}ring your bell
